        <p><i class="icon fa-solid fa-arrow-right fa-1x"></i>
           Polyalphabetic (Vigen√®re Cipher) cipher is much more stronger technique to encrypt your message than any of the other susbtitution encryption techniques. Simply because, here we use the key value in an efficient manner.</p>
      </div>
