    <div class="row">
      <div class="box steps col">
        <h2 class="box"><i class="icon fa-solid fa-hashtag fa-l"></i> Steps </h5>
        <ol>
          <li>Select any key.</li>
          <li>Repeat the key to get same length as the plain message. Suppose, plain text = 'thisisaplaintext'and the chosen key word is 'welcome' ,then key will be='welcomewelcomewelcom' </li>
          <li>Use this formula to encrypt: E[i]=(M[i]+k[i])%26,where 1 &lt i &lt length(plain message) and M[i],K[i] denotes the ascii value of the characters.</li>
          <li>Similarly, the decryption happens using the formula: D[i]=(M[i]-K[i])%26</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
   
